name: KaraandNate
0:
”Alexa, ask Kara an Nate where they are.”
”Alexa, ask Kara an Nate for an update.”
”Alexa, ask Kara an Nate how many countries they have left.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kara an nate
des: Popular YouTube travel-vlogers Kara and Nate are in a new country every week. This Alexa skill lets you keep up-to-date with what country they're in and how they're doing on their goal to visit 100 countries by 2019. You can now hear their latest update straight from their mouths! Simply say "Alexa, ask Kara an Nate for an update"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
